t;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;http://www.sscsr.gov.in/IMPORTANT-NOTICE-dt24022018.pdf\\&quot; target=\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE/NEWS &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;dt.&amp;nbsp; 24-02-2018&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;http://www.sscsr.gov.in/CGL2017-EXAMINATION-TIER-II-NOTICE-ABOUT-SCREEN-SHOTS-dt23022018.pdf\\&quot; target=\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE/NEWS (ABOUT CGL Examination 2017 (Tier-II)&amp;nbsp;)&amp;nbsp;dt.&amp;nbsp; 23-02-2018&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;http://www.sscsr.gov.in/IMPORTANT-NOTICE-dt21022018.pdf\\&quot; target=\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE/NEWS &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;dt.&amp;nbsp; 21-02-2018&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;http://www.sscsr.gov.in/IMPORTANT-NOTICE-dt21022018-ABOUT-CGLE2017-TIER-II.pdf\\&quot; target=\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE/NEWS (ABOUT CGL Examination 2017 (Tier-II)&amp;nbsp;)&amp;nbsp;dt.&amp;nbsp; 21-02-2018&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;http://www.sscsr.gov.in/IMPORTANT-NEWS-17022018.pdf\\&quot; target=\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE/NEWS &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;dt.&amp;nbsp; 17-02-2018&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;http://www.sscsr.gov.in/IMPORTANT-NEWS-15022018.pdf\\&quot; target=\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE/NEWS &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;dt.&amp;nbsp; 15-02-2018&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\\&quot;http://www.sscsr.gov.in/IMPORTANT-NEWS-31012018.pdf\\&quot; target=\\&quot;_blank\\&quot;&gt;IMPORTANT NOTICE/NEWS &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;dt.&amp;nbsp; 31-01-2018&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n
126	Contact us	&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Regional&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Director&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(Southern Region)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Staff Selection Commission,&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;2nd Floor, EVK Sampath Building,&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;DPI Campus, College Road,&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;CHENNAI &amp;ndash; 600 006&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Helpline Numbers :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPhone : 044-28251139&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMob: 09445195946&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Telephone Number :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(044) 2827 5568&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fax :&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; (044) 28270561&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;e-mail Id:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=\\&quot;mailto:sscsr.tn@nic.in\\&quot;&gt;sscsr.tn@nic.in&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	\N	\N	\N	\N	1	&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Regional&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Director&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(Southern Region)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Staff Selection Commission,&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;2nd Floor, EVK Sampath Building,&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;DPI Campus, College Road,&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;CHENNAI &amp;ndash; 600 006&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Helpline Numbers :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nPhone : 044-28251139&lt;br /&gt;\r\nMob: 09445195946&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Telephone Number :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(044) 2827 5568&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fax :&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; (044) 28270561&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;e-mail Id:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=\\&quot;mailto:sscsr.tn@nic.in\\&quot;&gt;sscsr.tn@nic.in&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n
138	Chairmen message	&lt;h1&gt;Recognition of Achievement&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This letter acknowledges the invaluable input &lt;strong&gt;you&lt;/strong&gt;, as a member of our Innovation Team,&amp;nbsp;have provided in the &amp;ldquo;Implement Rich Text Editor&amp;rdquo; project.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Management would like to hereby thank you for this great accomplishment that was delivered in a timely fashion, up to the highest company standards, and with great results:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table border=\\&quot;1\\&quot; cellspacing=\\&quot;\\\\&amp;quot;\\\\\\\\&amp;quot;0\\\\\\\\&amp;quot;\\\\&amp;quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;width:566px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;color:#c0392b\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Phase&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;color:#c0392b\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deadline&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;color:#c0392b\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Status&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p&gt;Phase 1: Market research&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;2021-04-15&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;✓&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p&gt;Phase 2: Editor implementation&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;2021-04-20&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;✓&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p&gt;Phase 3: Rollout to Production&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;2021-04-22&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;✓&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The project that you participated in is of utmost importance to the future success of our platform. We are very proud to share that the CKEditor implementation was a huge success and brought congratulations from both the key Stakeholders and the Customers:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This new editor has totally changed our content creation experience!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;mdash; John F. Smith, CEO, The New Web&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This letter recognizes that much of our success is directly attributable to your efforts. You deserve to be proud of your achievement. May your future efforts be equally successful and rewarding.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;I am sure we will be seeing and hearing a great deal more about your accomplishments in the future. Keep up the good work!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Best regards,&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Management&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n	\N	\N	\N	\N	1	&lt;h1&gt;Recognition of Achievement&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This letter acknowledges the invaluable input &lt;strong&gt;you&lt;/strong&gt;, as a member of our Innovation Team,&amp;nbsp;have provided in the &amp;ldquo;Implement Rich Text Editor&amp;rdquo; project.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The Management would like to hereby thank you for this great accomplishment that was delivered in a timely fashion, up to the highest company standards, and with great results:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;table border=\\&quot;1\\&quot; cellspacing=\\&quot;\\\\&amp;quot;\\\\\\\\&amp;quot;0\\\\\\\\&amp;quot;\\\\&amp;quot;\\&quot; style=\\&quot;width:566px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;color:#c0392b\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Phase&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;color:#c0392b\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deadline&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=\\&quot;color:#c0392b\\&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Status&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p&gt;Phase 1: Market research&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;2021-04-15&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;✓&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p&gt;Phase 2: Editor implementation&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;2021-04-20&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;✓&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;tr&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:268px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p&gt;Phase 3: Rollout to Production&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:124px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;2021-04-22&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;td style=\\&quot;width:152px\\&quot;&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;p style=\\&quot;text-align: center;\\&quot;&gt;✓&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\t\t\t&lt;/td&gt;\r\n\t\t&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n\t&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The project that you participated in is of utmost importance to the future success of our platform. We are very proud to share that the CKEditor implementation was a huge success and brought congratulations from both the key Stakeholders and the Customers:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This new editor has totally changed our content creation experience!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;mdash; John F. Smith, CEO, The New Web&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;This letter recognizes that much of our success is directly attributable to your efforts. You deserve to be proud of your achievement. May your future efforts be equally successful and rewarding.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;I am sure we will be seeing and hearing a great deal more about your accomplishments in the future. Keep up the good work!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Best regards,&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Management&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n
